      <title>马克龙任命埃里克·伦巴德为法国财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-23/macron-appoints-eric-lombard-as-french-finance-minister-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙任命埃里克·隆巴德为法国财政部长。隆巴德目前是法国储蓄银行集团的负责人。Benoit Berthelot 在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-23/macron-appoints-eric-lombard-as-french-finance-minister-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 18:59:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国债收益率小幅走高，长期债务不受青睐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/us-treasury-yields-edge-higher-with-long-term-debt-out-of-favor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员继续预计美联储明年降息步伐将放缓，且在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的领导下，美国财政状况可能进一步恶化，美国国债收益率周一上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/us-treasury-yields-edge-higher-with-long-term-debt-out-of-favor</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 18:46:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
